title: Snaps - Live from Walk-On’s in Baton Rouge
itunes:title: Snaps - Live from Walk-On’s in Baton Rouge
description:
Live and together from Walk-On’s Sports Bar and Bistreaux in Baton Rouge, Aaron and T-Bob discuss LSU’s chances against Ole Miss, UGA’s biggest potential stumbling block, and rail against the tyranny of Nick Saban and Alabama. #Volume #Herd #ColinCowherd
